findIntersectionCandidates

public List<CaliSmallElement> findIntersectionCandidates(CaliSmallElement element)
Finds all elements whose boundaries rectangle intersects with that of the argument element.

The fact that an element is returned by this method does not imply that the two elements actually overlap: they could be shaped in such a way that the enclosing rectangles intersect, but their actual contours do not.

Parameters:
element - the element of which all intersecting elements shall be found
Returns:
a (potentially empty) list containing all elements that can potentially intersect the argument element; the list is sorted by the X position of the elements
